.Dd November 20, 2023
.Dt ZINC 1
.Sh NAME
.Nm zinc
.Nd simple infinite canvas for X
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl hv
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
application provides you an infinite Y-axis canvas where you can draw with ease using the mouse. Nothing more. Nothing less.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl h
show usage
.It Fl v
display the program version
.El
.Sh KEYBOARD BINDINGS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Ctrl+c
Align the pizarra center with the window center.
.It Ctrl+z
Undo (If compiled with history support).
.It Ctrl+y
Redo (If compiled with history support).
.It r
Set color to red.
.It g
Set color to green.
.It b
Set color to blue.
.It w
Set color to white.
.It q
Set color to black.
.It o
Set color to orange.
.It y
Set color to yellow.
.It f
Set color to fuchsia.
.It t
Set color to teal.
.It c
Set color to cream.
.El
.Sh MOUSE BINDINGS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Left Mouse Button
Draw.
.It Right Mouse Button
Open the color selection tool.
.It Middle Mouse Button
Move around.
.It Scroll Up/Down
Scroll up/down.
.El
